0 WRO 2026 Senior — Barrier (black body + red ball, ×2)
0 Per the rules-PDF page 6 photo: 2 of the 4 barriers around the
0 mosaic area are black-bodied with a red ball on top. The
0 sister file ``senior_barrier_red_blue.ldr`` covers the other 2.
0 Authored with per-brick LDraw colour codes — LDraw 0 = black,
0 LDraw 4 = red — so the lego_prop tag does NOT pass a ``color``
0 attribute (which would override every brick uniformly and lose
0 the dual-colour scheme).
0
